text: Philippa "Pippa" Savage (born 15 March 1981 in Moree, New South Wales, Australia) is an Australian rower. She competed in the women's single sculls at the 2008 Summer Olympics. She did not compete at the 2012 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * * * * Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:Australian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Australia Category:Rowers at the 2008 Summer Olympics
